<h1>The Facts About Drug Abuse </h1>

<p><b>The Drug Abuse Council, 1980</b> </p>

<hr>

<p align="center"><font size="5"><b>Contents</b></font> </p>

<hr>

<p><a href="fadafwd.htm">Foreword </a>by Bethuel M. Webster </p>

<p><a href="fadadir.htm">Board of Directors of the Drug Abuse
Council</a> </p>

<ul>
    <li>Acknowledgments </li>
    <li>The Contributors </li>
</ul>

<p><a href="fadafin.htm">Final Report of the Drug Abuse Council</a>
</p>

<p><b>Staff Chapters:</b> </p>

<p>1. <a href="fada1.htm">The Federal Government's Response to
Illicit Drugs, 1969-1978 </a>by Peter Goldberg </p>

<p>2. <a href="fada2.htm">Drug-Law Enforcement Efforts</a> by
John R.Pekkanen </p>

