<h2>Drugs and our Community </h2>

<p>REPORT OF THE PREMIER'S DRUG ADVISORY COUNCIL MARCH 1996</p>

<p>Joint Departmental Information Centre
Cataloguing-in-Publication entry:</p>

<p>Victoria Premier's Drug Advisory Council Drugs and our
Community: Report of the Premier's Drug Advisory Council/
Premier's Drug Advisory Council, March 1996. </p>

<p>Melbourne: Victorian Government, 1996. 164 p.; 30 cm
Bibliography. ISBN: 0 7306 9227 2 Cover title. 1. Drug
utilization - Social aspects - Victoria. 2. Substance abuse -
Victoria. I. Title. 362.2909945 </p>

<p>Report designed and produced by O'SHEA SAUNDERS PTY. LTD. Tel:
(03) 9583 8827 </p>

<p>Cover designed and produced by ROYCE COMMUNICATIONS PTY. LTD.
Tel: (03) 9820 3733 </p>

<p>M A RC H 19 9 6 </p>

